{"tid":1437670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急!!] 810大埔遊行取消","createTime":"2019-08-09T14:59:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T16:20:32.000Z","uid":248492,"like":13,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7f6e2859ce23ca932075c76fba77b7b06c174527","tid":1437670,"uid":248492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:59:19.000Z","msg":"<strong>&lsquo;The demonstration is dead&rsquo;</strong><br />\n<br />\n很抱歉，810大埔遊行的反對通知書上訴失敗。我們始終不敵政府及警方的強權打壓，即使最後我們讓步至圍繞大埔運動場遊行，上訴委員會仍以「構成嚴重威脅公共秩序及公共安全」為由踐踏大埔居民的基本人權自由。這一次雞蛋敗給了高牆，辜負了大埔居民的熱切期待。對不起，我們失敗了。借用特首的一句說話，「810大埔遊行已壽終正寢」。在高牆不惜一切的堵塞下，民意始終走不出連儂隧道，但哪裡有壓迫，哪裡便有抗爭。如我們一開始的宣言所說，民意是不能被消滅，亦不會被束縛，因為這只會使民意更加壯大。我們深信，民意總有一天能掙開枷鎖，擺脫束縛，衝出隧道。總有一天，我們能在隧道外相見。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>We will be back, and we shall never surrender!</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2443992782323646/posts/2471304949592429/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2443992782323646%2Fposts%2F2471304949592429%2F&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrKpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=4ce39722\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2443992782323646/posts/2471304949592429/</a>"},{"pid":"a6950e26c5811eb6fcab07a094b4db66d7b0e723","tid":1437670,"uid":248492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:59:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14539931cac9199710d1eb6977db132fb08069a7","tid":1437670,"uid":248492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:00:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24171459b7b2b64cc9d04e67a659ec935b96ae2b","tid":1437670,"uid":248492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:00:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1107b661864271ef6410143bb8e20cfe4db93fa1","tid":1437670,"uid":186297,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:12:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RpU5HTO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRpU5HTO.jpg&h=86a